description:
Get ready for Happy Happy Pack,
a new downloadable content pack for Party Party Time!
Enjoy 10 brand new minigames!
Gather everyone and party happy, party on!

The Happy Happy Pack includes the following content:

10 New Minigames:
6 Competitive Games
- Strike Spin
- Arrow Aim
- Ball Darts
- High and Low
- Quick Draw
- Shoot to Score
4 Co-op Games
- Boss Fight
- Floating Blocks
- Sheep Herding
- Block Fit
name: Happy Happy Pack
